<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ي ق ظ:</span> رَجُلٌ <span class="c2">(يَقِظٌ)</span> بِضَمِّ الْقَافِ وَكَسْرِهَا أَيْ <span class="c2">(مُتَيَقِّظٌ)</span> حَذِرٌ. وَ <span class="c2">(أَيْقَظَهُ)</span> مِنْ نَوْمِهِ نَبَّهَهُ <span class="c2">(فَتَيَقَّظَ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(اسْتَيْقَظَ)</span> فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(يَقْظَانُ)</span> ، وَالِاسْمُ <span class="c2">(الْيَقَظَةُ)</span> بِفَتْحَتَيْنِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>